To scale down the etcd deployment, perform a normal upgrade and set the *statefulset.replicaCount* value to the desired number of nodes. For example, use the command below to reduce the cluster to a single replica:

~~~
$ helm upgrade bitnami/etcd \
  --set statefulset.replicaCount=1
~~~
